content.rendered:
Directed by Chakri Toleti. Richard Harris. Jasmine Kaur

Written by Dheeraj Rattan

Cast Sonakshi Sinha (Jeenal Patel). Diljit Dosanjh (Teji). Karan Johar (Karan / Arjun). Lara Dutta (Sophia). Boman Irani (Mr. Garry). Salman Khan (Self). Sammy Jonas Heaney (Jonathon Jonas (as Sammy John Heaney)) . Abhinav (Diljit’s Friend). Heena Achhra (AD Model). Adam (Security Guy 1). Chirague Amarchande (Thug). Raj Awasti (Airport Passenger / Awards Attendee). Karishma Bhandari (Air India Hostess). Alia Bhatt (Cameo appearance). Kerrieanne Booker (Airport Passenger). Sonny Chatrath (Investor). Krishna Chaturvedi (Nilesh). Mukesh Chhabra (AD Director). Rene Costa (Hotel Guest). Rana Daggubati (Rana Daggubati). Samer Singh Dawar (Security (as Chirag Dawar)). Aditi Desai (Grand Mother). Riteish Deshmukh (Riteish). Karan Singh Duggall (Tug 2). Jay Gandhi (Airport – Traveller). Nasir Ghaffar (Thug). Apurva Gondalia (Journalist at IiFA Green Carpet). Leon Gonzalez (Self). Sonia Goswami (Airport Passenger). Naman Gupta (IIFA Crew Member). Richard Harris (Volunteer). Thomas Jackson (Goon). Dolly Jagdeo (Airport Passenger / Awards Attendee). Gurnita Kaur Kahlon (Conference Assistant, Ceremony Attendee). Katrina Kaif (Katrina Kaif). Aditya Roy Kapoor (Aditya). Raja Kayani (Security Guy). Arbaaz Khan (Arbaaz Khan). Hassan Khan (Gangster Arjun). Sohail Khan (Sohail Khan). Wazid Khan (Thug). Pawan Kudesan (Diljit’s Friend). Noor Lila (Hotel Guest (as Shabnam Karimzada)). Swaylee Loughnane (Roz). Alpesh Malaviya (Airport Passenger). Soni Marwah (Airport Passenger). Kevin Matadeen (Hotel Guest). Melody (Airhostess). Bharat Mistri (Airport Passenger). Ray Neville (Paparazzi). Stephen Owen (Goon). Esha Patel (Airport Passenger). Hardik Patel (Security Guy). Hiten Patel (Raj Hotel Manager). Vihaan Patel (Airport Passenger). Neha Pushp (Fan at Airport). Saima Qureshi (Journalist). Hamaz Raja (Writer). Khushi Rajput (Young Girl). Amrit Randava (Diljit’s Friend). Ijaz Rashid (Thug). Ariana Sajnani (Annie). Sanjana G. Sandhu (Airport Check in Attendent). Harmeet Sangi (Lady tenent (as Harmeet Sanghi)). Viraf Sarkari (Sponsor). Anna Satchit (Airport Passenger). Liam Scott (Goon). Nathaniel Scott (Goon). Divya Sethi (Natasha). Atul Sharma (Airport Passenger / Awards Attendee). Vinita Sharma (Airport Passenger). Rajendra Shashtri (Grand Father). Aman Sher (Diljit’s Friend). Sushant Singh Rajput (Self). Jonathan Staples (Goon). Wei-Chen Sun (Bar Customer). Gillian Vassilliou (Reporter). Virendra (Security). Umesh Wadhvani (Thug 4). Rina Yadav (Airport Passenger). Zivile Matikiene (Rich Blond lady in New York (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Jackky Bhagnani. Vashu Bhagnani. Sam Bhattacharjee. Ritcha Bhushan. Shoaib Ibrahim. Sameer Qasim Isa. Firuzi Khan. Nasir Khan. Arun Kumar. Kapil Madnani. Farid Malick. Adib Malik. Yogiraj Shetty. Nitin Upadhyaya

Production Indo-UK Film Compan. Jhakaa. Lola’s Production
